{"type":"message","id":"93ed0099","parentId":"d33de08a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:48:31.300Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6puo6x9gce1m_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"* 8547471 Merge origin/develop into fix/auth-registration-ui + fix LicenseCategory type mismatch between services\n*   a8cf208 Merge branch 'fix/auth-registration-ui' into 'develop'\n|\\  \n| * 3a6e2c2 about: edit .gitlab-ci.yml\n| * 182b2d2 about: edit .gitlab-ci.yml\n* | 3da33a5 chore: update yarn.lock\n* |   3259abe Merge branch 'feat/database-master' into 'develop'\n|\\ \\  \n* \\ \\   153bb54 Merge branch 'feat/database-master' into 'develop'\n|\\ \\ \\  \n| | | | * 7fd4ce9 WIP on auth-registration-ui: bcd486d feat(settings): load license categories from API instead of empty settings\n| | | |/| \n| | | | * e9b98a8 index on auth-registration-ui: bcd486d feat(settings): load license categories from API instead of empty settings\n| | | |/  \n| | | * bcd486d feat(settings): load license categories from API instead of empty settings\n| | | * 6ab29de fix(auth-ui): correct login icon and add address/identity_card fields to register form\n| | |/  \n| | * ebac17c fix: move import out of function params in AddDatModal and ScheduleModal\n| | * 4e021c8 fix: move import out of function params in 3 modal components\n| | * 25b1a50 responsive: implement responsive for desktop, tablet, mobile and another screen"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":141,"aggregated":"* 8547471 Merge origin/develop into fix/auth-registration-ui + fix LicenseCategory type mismatch between services\n*   a8cf208 Merge branch 'fix/auth-registration-ui' into 'develop'\n|\\  \n| * 3a6e2c2 about: edit .gitlab-ci.yml\n| * 182b2d2 about: edit .gitlab-ci.yml\n* | 3da33a5 chore: update yarn.lock\n* |   3259abe Merge branch 'feat/database-master' into 'develop'\n|\\ \\  \n* \\ \\   153bb54 Merge branch 'feat/database-master' into 'develop'\n|\\ \\ \\  \n| | | | * 7fd4