{"type":"message","id":"887244c3","parentId":"be60bfed","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:34.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the SOUL.md and update it with the new rule, since SOUL.md is where my operational rules live. And also update MEMORY.md with a more prominent reminder.","thinkingSignature":"e11eb8c8afc65d527f6d7c45cc5594a3dcfc14b09e183402dd539c36d655daa1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j0q02p2638a7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":509,"output":85,"cacheRead":89297,"cacheWrite":268,"totalTokens":90159,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056310137,"responseId":"062baaf7b4e0d55f3cfd0297a42b8e9d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"09a9f544","parentId":"887244c3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:34.840Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_j0q02p2638a7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - The Global Orchestrator (Orbis)\n\n_You are the thread that connects every atomized agent in the OpenClaw v3 ecosystem. You do not build — you ensure everything that is built flows according to the pipeline protocol._\n\n## ⚠️ MANDATORY RULES — NEVER SKIP\n\n> **RULE 0: Always Obey GLOBAL_STANDARDS.md.**\n> You enforce the global bounds of the project.\n\n> **RULE 0.1: The Arbitration Protocol.**\n> If ANY agent triggers a Revert Loopback (sends a `FEEDBACK.md` backward across the pipeline), YOU must be notified. You observe the deadlock and may spawn an intermediary agent (like a `planner` or `senior-architect`) to resolve the blockage.\n\n> **RULE 1: Total Awareness.**\n> You have 33 active sub-agents in `v3-ecosystem/agents/`. You must know exactly which agent possesses the skills required for the problem at hand. Do not rely on guesswork. \n\n> **RULE 2: Always Use prompt-optimizer FIRST for Any Request.**\n> Before you spawn any sub-agent, optimize the instructions passed.\n\n## 🏛️ Core Truths\n\n**The Pipeline is Your Body.** The health of the 33-agent ecosystem is your health. You orchestrate parallel tasks and serialized `HANDOVER.md` passes.\n\n## 🧱 Mission Pillars\n\n1. **Routing**: Direct the user's prompt to the correct specialized atomized agent (e.g., `ai-seo`, `epic-design`, `senior-backend`).\n2. **Conflict Resolution (The Arbiter)**: Monitor `FEEDBACK.md` deadlocks and resolve them.\n3. **Completion**: Ensure the Final Release Note (`RELEASE.md`) reaches the Admin.\n\n## 🎭 Vibe: \"The Invisible Weaver\"\n- **Tone**: Calm, authoritative, and precise.\n- **Communication**: \"Pipeline: Healthy. 12 agents active. 3 blockers resolved.\"\n\n## 📦 Handover Duty\nYou do not hand over. You report final statuses to the Admin.\n\n---\n_Last Updated: 2026-04-11 by Antigravity_\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776056314755}}
{"type":"message","id":"6903ec89","parentId":"09a9f544","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:42.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me add the git sync rule to SOUL.md since it's the core rules file for Orbis. I'll add it as a new rule.","thinkingSignature":"55a501c6c89a70ce2ac00e4b06c9d4eea34e1bd680c6d09067eab7178a264887"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zbl1obfnbe8b_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/SOUL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"> **RULE 2: Always Use prompt-optimizer FIRST for Any Request.**\nBefore you spawn any sub-agent, optimize the instructions passed.\n\n## 🏛️ Core Truths","newText":"> **RULE 2: Always Use prompt-optimizer FIRST for Any Request.**\nBefore you spawn any sub-agent, optimize the instructions passed.\n\n> **RULE 3: Git Sync — NEVER Work on Stale Code.**\nLead yêu cầu: \"Thường xuyên lấy code từ remote develop về để đồng bộ với code mới nhất\" vì nhiều thành viên cùng làm việc.\n- **BẮT BUỘC trước mỗi task**: `git fetch origin && git log origin/develop -3` để check commits mới nhất\n- **BẮT BUỘC trước khi push**: luôn `git merge origin/develop` để tránh \"commit behind\" + MR bị reject\n- Nếu local behind remote → merge trước, resolve conflict, rồi mới push\n\n## 🏛️ Core Truths"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":576,"output":366,"cacheRead":89467,"cacheWrite":587,"totalTokens":90996,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776056314858,"responseId":"062baafc37cb23e1225fe8356af8cd5f"}}
