{"type":"message","id":"9db73abc","parentId":"93bfa523","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:05:07.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can't access the GitLab API directly. Let me try a different approach - check if there's any environment file that sets the API URL for the Docker deployment, or check the remote server directly.Actually, let me think about this differently. The FE dev server (localhost:3000) when started locally, uses `.env.local` which has `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1`. The browser would call that URL.\n\nBut the deployed FE might have `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` baked in differently. Since the CI/CD does `docker compose up --build`, it builds the Next.js app during deployment. \n\nIf `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` isn't set in the docker-compose environment, the build falls back to the default `http://127.0.0.1:5002/api/v1`, which would fail in production since there's no local backend. The real problem is that GitLab CI/CD variables aren't set up correctly for this project, so the frontend build is using the wrong backend URL.\n\nI need to tell the Lead that `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` needs to be configured as a CI/CD variable in GitLab or in the docker-compose.yml file, otherwise the frontend won't know where to find the backend API.","thinkingSignature":"fe9ce3b10ff207a038be1975b81d561c82ad0aa671488caa5fa8d48649759e01"},{"type":"text","text":"Nguyên nhân tìm thấy rồi!\n\n**Root cause:** `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` không được set trong GitLab CI/CD khi build. Next.js đóng gói biến `NEXT_PUBLIC_` **lúc build**, nên FE dùng fallback `http://127.0.0.1:5002` — và `:8686` trong lỗi là cổng không hợp lệ.\n\n**Cần fix ở 2 nơi:**\n\n### 1. GitLab CI/CD Variables\nVào **Project Settings → CI/CD → Variables** thêm:\n```\nKey: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL\nValue: http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1\nType: Variable\nMasked: No\n```\n\n### 2. Cập nhật `.gitlab-ci.yml` để pass biến vào Docker build\n```yaml\n# Trong stage deploy, thêm:\nscript:\n  - cd $PRJ_PATH\n  - NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://103.253.21.139:5002/api/v1 docker compose up -d --build\n```\n\nSau khi Lead thêm biến GitLab, re-run pipeline deploy là xong.\n\n**Mình cần quyền GitLab để tự thêm biến CI/CD không?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":127,"output":562,"cacheRead":100461,"cacheWrite":590,"totalTokens":101740,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776056694675,"responseId":"062bac78c2fb0b4920297a548e63003a"}}
